may well have been influenced also by the common Irish surname derived from the medieval Norman male name.  See also  Joss ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Queen Joyce de Balladon of Gwent was born in 0890, in Abergavenny, Monmouthshire, Wales, her father, Hamlin De Balladon, was 21 and her mother, Mrs Hamlin de Baladon, was 16. She married King Ynyr ab Owain of Gwent in Glamorgan, Wales. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died on 1 September 0989, in Glamorgan, Wales, at the age of 99."},"et":{"0890–1 September 0989":"0890–1. september 0989","0890–0989":"0890–0989","0890–0935":"0890–0935","0918–1019":"0918–1019","0870–Male":"0870–Surnud","0874–Female":"0874–Surnud","1019":"1019","0874":"0874","4 April 0944":"4. aprill 0944","0918":"0918","0870":"0870","0890":"0890","1 September 0989":"1. september 0989","0989":"0989","0935":"0935","Gwent, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales","Gwent Castle, Gwent, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Gwent, Wales, United Kingdom","Abergavenny, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Abergavenny, Monmouthshire, Wales","Albergvenny, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales, United Kingdom","Gwent, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales","Gwent Castle, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales"},"fi":{"0890–1 September 0989":"0890–1. syyskuuta 0989","0890–0989":"0890–0989","0890–0935":"0890–0935","0918–1019":"0918–1019","0870–Male":"0870–Kuollut","0874–Female":"0874–Kuollut","1019":"1019","0874":"0874","4 April 0944":"4. huhtikuuta 0944","0918":"0918","0870":"0870","0890":"0890","1 September 0989":"1. syyskuuta 0989","0989":"0989","0935":"0935","Gwent, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales","Gwent Castle, Gwent, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Gwent, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Abergavenny, Monmouthshire, Wales":"Abergavenny, Monmouthshire, Wales","Albergvenny, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Gwent, Glamorganshire, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales","Gwent Castle, Glamorgan, Wales":"Glamorgan, Wales"},"fr":{"0890–1 September 0989":"0